page.title: 09FLORA
page.content: Plants found in the area include: tulip,marigold,dog rose,lilac,campion, dahlia,pansy,forget me not,ragwort, daisy,poppy,wood anemone,rose,caraway, rose bay willow herb,silver weed,dock, daffodil,cowslip,crocus,hopvine,ivy, primrose,moon daisy,mistletoe,thistle, foxglove,dandelion,oxeye daisy,mallow, sweet violet,teasel,buttercup,balsam, white dead-nettle,cowparsley,sorrel, white and red clover,stinging nettle. Silverbirch,willow,ash,elm,apple, sweet chestnut,yew,horse chestnut,oak, poplar,conifer,pine,juniper,larch, holly,sycamore,gean,crab apple,cherry, laburnum,blackthorn,rowan,hawthorn, elder,bay,birch,alder,hazel,beech,fir, scots pine,spruce,lime,cedar,maple, pear,damson,plum,bramble and grape. Wheat,oats,barley,maize,seed-rape, peas.
